page.title: 06A WHEATHAMPSTEAD BOY
page.content: We change for games and it ends at 3:25p.m then we go home at 3:30p.m.I change my trousers and go up Nicholas's house to play marbles.Then I go back home at 5:00 p.m I have my tea.Then I go up Nicholas's to play marbles and come back at 6:50p.m.Then I get changed for judo and I go back to Nicholas's and we walk down to judo.Judo starts at 7:30p.m and ends at 8:30p.m Nicholas's mum picks us up and she drops me at my house.I go in to my house and watch the rest of Quincy on the television.Then I get ready for bed and then I go to bed.
